{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/Sailing_Ship.gif?t=1672784119\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An Adventure Like No Other</h2>January, 1928. The SS Carolina is lost deep in the ocean. There's a deadly chill outside. The captain is hiding something from you. By night 2 you're attacked and the crew is missing! It's a nightmare!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/Code.gif?t=1672784119\" /><br>You play as 2nd Officer Walton. Explore the ship, use items, find the crew, and try to survive! You must get back to land and not let the ship sink.<br><br>This is a completely new experience from the creators of SimAirport and SimCasino!<br><br><strong>Art by lunaanandi</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2066300/extras/Lifeboat.gif?t=1672784119\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A point and click adventure game with a horror twist!<br></li><li>Beautiful, retro pixel art style with a nautical theme!<br></li><li>Hunt for crucial items and use them to survive and rid the curse!<br></li><li>Classically designed logical game mechanics with a modern UI for a satisfying experience.<br></li><li>Discover the truth and unlock multiple endings!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ship Shape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2066300/aebaa22985a979684fc5f4022142ff23b0dfe688.jpg"},{"name":"Kick in the Right Direction","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2066300/7162c0cd6f9ba13124addeb068ab4cf33eafc097.jpg"},{"name":"Secrets Within","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2066300/9b2ec19f4b1b7f7edc8295888e1c136fa578eb8b.jpg"},{"name":"Smooth Sailing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.co